on gametest cycle f safe1 context:
    set {cyclef::safe1::value::before} to string value of lane-f-safe1-valued
    set string value of lane-f-safe1-valued to "beta"
    set {cyclef::safe1::value::after_set} to string value of lane-f-safe1-valued
    delete string value of lane-f-safe1-valued
    set {cyclef::safe1::value::after_delete} to string value of lane-f-safe1-valued
